    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3222680/extras/1dd14785ce6582f4357d8397ca34c164.poster.avif?t=1728624905\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3222680/extras/1dd14785ce6582f4357d8397ca34c164.webm?t=1728624905\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3222680/extras/1dd14785ce6582f4357d8397ca34c164.mp4?t=1728624905\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏介绍</h2><br><br>14世纪，伊比利亚半岛的收复故土运动接近尾声。玩家将以桌游式的玩法重新决定半岛的命运。<br>格拉纳达，曾经是穆斯林治下安达卢斯的霸主，数经战乱，如今处于风中残烛之境。<br>而基督三国：卡斯蒂利亚，阿拉贡，葡萄牙，现已抛下圣战的面具，剑指霸权，互不相让。<br>伊比利亚半岛正当四国逐鹿时代，玩家将选择其中之一来平定战乱。<br><br>游戏提供两种胜利方式：一是占领最多的领土，二是在四个国家全部参战的会战中获得三次胜利。<br><br>各个国家的士兵有固有的特色，其中贵族兵牌只能由所属的国家获得，民兵和重装兵则任何国家都能获得。<br>卡斯蒂利亚：较高的防御力，所有属性整体优秀<br>阿拉贡：较高的防御力，强大的近战单位<br>葡萄牙：强大的远程单位，薄弱的近战单位<br>格拉纳达：属性整体上平庸且严重依赖贵族卡牌，但兼顾近战和远程<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏框架</h2>1.\t王国阶段<br>王国阶段是玩家决定自己的战略选择的阶段。这个阶段采取典型的桌游形式的操作：掷骰子，选择移动方向，在到达地选择这个回合的行为：获取卡牌，征服，祈祷。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3222680/extras/626bb2cd56bb8c323c80081c535d2ca8.poster.avif?t=1728624905\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3222680/extras/626bb2cd56bb8c323c80081c535d2ca8.webm?t=1728624905\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3222680/extras/626bb2cd56bb8c323c80081c535d2ca8.mp4?t=1728624905\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>2.\t卡牌构筑<br>在王国阶段，玩家可以通过拖拽单位卡牌来控制军队的布置顺序。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3222680/extras/beddc0055bf2b404a65f0480a1870960.poster.avif?t=1728624905\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3222680/extras/beddc0055bf2b404a65f0480a1870960.webm?t=1728624905\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3222680/extras/beddc0055bf2b404a65f0480a1870960.mp4?t=1728624905\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>3.\t战斗阶段<br>战斗阶段会根据桌面战棋的规则自动进行。玩家需要观察战斗阶段的走向来改善卡牌布置顺序，以获得最终胜利。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3222680/extras/1dd14785ce6582f4357d8397ca34c164.poster.avif?t=1728624905\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3222680/extras/1dd14785ce6582f4357d8397ca34c164.webm?t=1728624905\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3222680/extras/1dd14785ce6582f4357d8397ca34c164.mp4?t=1728624905\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >多人游戏</h2>可以通过本地多人游戏或者steam Remote play进行多人竞争。",
